data.description: Sturdy 3 Bedrooms, 1 full bath, 1 half bath with open Den/Dining/Kitchen layout. Original refinished hardwoods in living room,carpet in two bedrooms. Energy efficient windows throughout! Large corner Lot with nice storage building in the back yard. 2 car covered parking and single car garage, all with electric! Pecan Trees for the perfect shaded yard! Overton ISD, near the lake, park, and High Hill Golf Course. Come through!
